verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Just as I am, poor wretched, blind;
Sight, riches, healing of the mind,
Yea, all I need in Thee to find,
O Lamb of God, I come.  I come.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Just as I am Your love unknown
Hath broken every barrier down;
Now to be Yours, Yes, Yours alone,
O Lamb of God, I come.  I come.{/lang-eng}
